track.name: The Nearness of You
comments: Hoagy Carmichael wrote this one, an old classic.

So warm and comforting.

Norah's voice is heavenly
In England only last week........... appeared on Jools Holland's' Later with 'show.. and was very good. As ever. Her dad is 91 now, has hopefully stopped 'rutting' now...
There is nothing so good, as the nearness of you. Wherever you are now..............
yea - i think perhaps there are better songs for her talents. this song just bores the crap out of me.

This is what love is all about, to be able to care for some one and have that someone care for you is what love is all about, there is no problem that can't be worked out with understanding, caring and the nearness of you.
